{
  "title": "Thiết lập quy trình sản xuất của bạn",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Thiết lập quy trình sản xuất của bạn</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Các công cụ và quy trình nâng cao hiệu quả phát triển trong Unreal Engine</p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Setting Up Your Production Pipeline\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/04ce5735-1232-400e-b1c1-1fa8ba176b66?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/04ce5735-1232-400e-b1c1-1fa8ba176b66?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/04ce5735-1232-400e-b1c1-1fa8ba176b66?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><p>Việc thiết lập quy trình sản xuất cho phép các nhà phát triển đưa các chuyên gia có bộ kỹ năng đa dạng vào quy trình sản xuất của nhóm -- và Unreal Engine cung cấp các công cụ và tính năng cho nhiều quy trình công việc khác nhau, đảm bảo luồng nội dung và phát triển tính năng ổn định. Để tìm hiểu thêm, hãy đọc về các chủ đề sau.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"topics\">chủ đề</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Unreal Turnkey simplifies platform setup by automating SDK installation and management.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:automating-platform-and-sdk-management-with-unreal-turnkey\" page-name=\"Unreal Turnkey\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/7d03422b-9b74-46ce-8e07-be10d230ad0a/platformmanagementwithunrealturnkeytopicimage.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Learn about caching data to save your team's time and disk space.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-derived-data-cache-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Derived Data Cache (DDC)\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/119079f7-54f4-48f3-9eaf-48812db25f5b/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Explore ways to use the ushell command line interface in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:how-to-use-ushell-for-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Ushell\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2fa5c521-42c0-442c-983d-1405239fbf57/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Learn more about this flexible storage solution for Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:zen-storage-server-for-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Zen Storage Server\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/4343cd99-ae34-41ff-9c98-d5d5557f05e1/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Reference material for Unreal Engine's build pipeline\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-the-unreal-engine-build-pipeline\" page-name=\"Unreal Build Pipeline\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/407151ed-0efe-4205-ab74-43bd3270c4dc/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A recommended naming convention to help organize your Assets.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:recommended-asset-naming-conventions-in-unreal-engine-projects\" page-name=\"Recommended Asset Naming Conventions\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/68968ba4-2397-49fd-9a71-965501cf348f/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Learn the ways that you can deploy Unreal Engine either to individual users or your organization.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:deploying-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Deploying Unreal Engine\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/67559e46-f9d4-4a23-94c6-4a6676c8e563/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"How to setup Perforce or SVN so that you can share assets with other on your team.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:collaboration-and-version-control-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Collaboration and Version Control in Unreal Engine\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/faf7f919-d6e6-452e-a9cd-90e0ad2bad06/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Get multiple users on different computers into a shared Unreal Editor session, collaborating live to build content together.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:multi-user-editing-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Multi-User Editing in Unreal Engine\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2b6f163b-4521-4112-a24e-0ccfdcc6906e/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"How to create Unreal Engine plugins.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:plugins-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Plugins\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e56ad6d8-dc67-4936-9f8c-de019010d4a4/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Virtualize assets to improve the efficiency of source control pulls for your team.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:virtual-assets-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Virtual Assets\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/01ba8554-a941-4a39-876f-c72b1a739bf1/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Objects that redirect references for moved assets from their old location to their new location.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:asset-redirectors-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Redirectors\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/6f327375-0c11-4fce-bb1a-38cc2edabccc/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Introduction to using Blueprints and Python to control the Unreal Editor programmatically.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:scripting-and-automating-the-unreal-editor\" page-name=\"Scripting and Automating the Unreal Editor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/19ca577d-38d1-4602-8247-52fc819ad8e4/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Describes how to use Unreal with the Autodesk ShotGrid integration.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-unreal-engine-with-autodesk-shotgrid\" page-name=\"Using Unreal Engine with Autodesk ShotGrid\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/62d48d11-5396-45fb-8d24-8e3858d69f01/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An infrastructure to improve your team's workflow.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:horde-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Horde\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/377a8914-7a1d-453f-96bd-9085e6cf1474/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
